; Coverage for history.cc lines 300-330: map_prices function
; The pricedb command calls map_prices to enumerate all price entries
; This exercises the price map iteration and time-based filtering

P 2024/01/01 EUR $1.10
P 2024/02/01 EUR $1.15
P 2024/03/01 EUR $1.08

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses:Travel    500 EUR
    Assets:Checking

test pricedb --now 2024/04/01
P 2024/01/01 00:00:00 EUR $1.10
P 2024/02/01 00:00:00 EUR $1.15
P 2024/03/01 00:00:00 EUR $1.08
end test
